itunes:summary:
Miss Issa is making moves, Mirror B*tch is back, and there might be a new boo on the horizon. Join Crissle and Fran as they weigh in on this week’s play by play of HBO’s Insecure. 

Participate in the conversation on social media using the hashtag #InsecuriTEA. Don’t forget to follow @InsecureHBO and @LSNPodcasts.
